to tell the second guy

24:09.281 --> 24:11.613
how he feels
and how he appreciates

24:11.750 --> 24:14.742
what the second guy
did for the first guy.

24:14.887 --> 24:16.377
Chach, forget all these guys.

24:16.522 --> 24:20.857
You want to say thank you,
you say, "Thank you."

24:20.993 --> 24:22.757
Thank you, Fonz.

24:22.895 --> 24:25.865
