cousins are for?

24:25.998 --> 24:27.864
See you later.

24:28.000 --> 24:30.162
- Hi, Rich.
- Hey, Chach.

24:30.302 --> 24:33.397
Fonz, did you have a talk
with Chachi?

24:33.539 --> 24:36.133
Yeah, yeah, I did.

24:36.275 --> 24:37.470
